nodes.text: The Tusken's Eye was a G-class star in the Tusken's Eye system, orbited by a cloudy planet where the Dark Nest resided following the destruction of Kr. It was here that fifteen nest ships were built: one for Gorog and one for each of the fourteen nests that abandoned the Utegetu Nebula in 36 ABY.

With the help from Jae Juun and Tarfang, Luke Skywalker and Han Solo traced the Dark Nest from Woteba to the Eye aboard the DR919a. There they infiltrated the Gorog nest ship as the nest ships jumped to the Murgo Choke to engage an Alliance blockade.
